  "2026-07-13T15:32:34.614Z",codex-sdk-contracts-20260713,"Evidence: runDeps now reuses collectDanglingDependencyReferences with the runtime terminal registry and projects parent/blocked_by misses as typed edges in tree, graph, and summary. Unit and deleted-parent acceptance tests passed; installed tarball reported missing_count=1. Delete remains permissive by documented compatibility decision."
  "2026-07-13T16:06:26.450Z",codex-sdk-contracts-20260713,"Review follow-up: actively addressing current-head Gemini findings for this item's implementation surface in PR #545. The item is reopened only for the duration of the review fix and will be reverified, closed, and released after evidence is recorded."
  "2026-07-13T16:15:48.810Z",codex-sdk-contracts-20260713,"Review evidence: dependency projection now trims identifiers, canonicalizes relationship kind casing, and deduplicates kind/id pairs case-insensitively. A legacy mixed-case stored-id regression passes through the public runDeps surface; malformed non-string rows are excluded upstream by item loading, so no unreachable second validator was added."
